title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10 ยง 756.2 - Medical director
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10 ยง 756.2 - Medical director

State Regulations

In addition to the requirements set forth in section
751.4
of this Title, if the
medical director is not an obstetrician/gynecologist who meets the definition
of a qualified specialist as set forth in section
700.2
of this Title, there shall
be consultation from an obstetrician/gynecologist in the development of
policies and procedures governing the provision of abortion
services. Notes
